properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const s3 = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('ikfkfreeksides').value[0];const c2 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C2 Group')('Contents')('C2').size[0] * 0.5;const c1 = thisProperty.propertyGroup(4)('C1 Group')('Contents')('C1').size[0] * 0.5;let A, r3a, r3b, r3aboff, hioff;try {    A = Math.acos(thisLayer.clamp((c1 - c2) / s3, -1, 1));    r3a = [-(c2 * Math.sin(A)), -(s3 + c2 * Math.cos(A))];    r3b = [-(c1 * Math.sin(A)), -(c1 * Math.cos(A))];} catch (err) {    value;}const dist = thisLayer.effect('Muscles')('Upper Bulge');const zp = [0, 0];const tang = [(s3 * 0.2) * Math.cos(A), (s3 * 0.2) * Math.sin(A)]const ms = thisLayer.effect('Muscles')('Style');if (ms == 1) {    hioff = 0.66;    const r3ab = [r3a[0] + ((r3b[0] - r3a[0]) * hioff), r3a[1] + ((r3b[1] - r3a[1]) * hioff)];    r3aboff = r3ab + [dist * Math.cos(-A - 1.5708), dist * Math.sin(-A - 1.5708)];    const uo = (thisLayer.effect('Muscles')('Upper Offset (Leg style only)') * 0.005) + 0.5    const r3abR = r3ab * uo + r3aboff * (1 - uo);    const r3abL = r3aboff * uo + r3ab * (1 - uo);    createPath(points = [        [-r3a[0], r3a[1]], r3a, r3abR, r3b, [-r3b[0], r3b[1]], [-r3abL[0], r3abL[1]]],        inTangents = [[tang[0], tang[1]], zp, [tang[0], -tang[1]], zp, zp, [tang[0], tang[1]]],        outTangents = [zp, [-tang[0], tang[1]], [-tang[0], tang[1]], zp, zp, [-tang[0], -tang[1]]],        is_closed = true)} else {    hioff = 0.45;    r3aboff = (r3a + r3b) * hioff + [dist * Math.cos(-A - 1.5708), dist * Math.sin(-A - 1.5708)];    thisProperty.createPath(points = [        [-r3a[0], r3a[1]], r3a, r3aboff, r3b, [-r3b[0], r3b[1]], [-r3aboff[0], r3aboff[1]]],        inTangents = [[tang[0], tang[1]], zp, [tang[0], -tang[1]], [tang[0], -tang[1]], zp, [tang[0], tang[1]]],        outTangents = [zp, [-tang[0], tang[1]], [-tang[0], tang[1]], zp, [-tang[0], -tang[1]], [-tang[0], -tang[1]]],        is_closed = true)}
